      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks, that's a good start. Could you make it sound a bit less \"template\" though? Specifically, maybe add a sentence or two acknowledging how much we enjoyed the culture fit during the interview, just to show we actually liked him as a person. Keep it professional though, I don't want it to sound unprofessional or too casual.",
