    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Your Application for the Senior Dev Role\n\nDear Marcus,\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I wanted to personally reach out to you regarding your recent application for the Senior Dev role at our Austin-based company. We were genuinely impressed by your skills and enthusiasm, and it was a pleasure to learn more about your background and experiences.\n\nAfter careful consideration and thorough evaluation, we have decided to move forward with another candidate who has more experience with our specific cloud architecture. This decision was not easy, as Marcus is a talented and dedicated professional. We truly appreciate the time and effort you invested in the application process, and we wish you the best in your future endeavors.\n\nI must say, during our interview, Marcus truly stood out to us. His passion for technology and his ability to connect with our team culture made a lasting impression. We enjoyed getting to know him, and we believe he would have been a great addition to our team.\n\nWe encourage you to apply for future opportunities with us, as we believe you have the potential to excel in many roles. Thank you once again for your interest in our company, and we wish you continued success in your career.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]\n[Your Position]\n[Company Name]",
